         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#jmr"><head>Translations</head>
         <p>Marcus Aurelius Gounthassos, in exchange for being saved, I set (this) up</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#cmr"><head>Translations</head>
            <p>I, Markos Aurelios Gounthas <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign xml:lang="la">Marcus Aurelius</foreign></supplied>, having been rescued, dedicated <supplied reason="subaudible">this</supplied> to Him who saved me.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" source="#AE">
            <p>Moi, Marcus Aurelius Gounthas, sauvé, j’ai fait une dédicace à qui m’a sauvé.</p>
         </div></div>
